Starscream

Starscream responded to Phobia.

"We're on our way." He turned to the Lavacons, "Come with me! The 
battle awaits!"

Starscream took off towards the Pred cave.
______________________________________________________________________
Prebon

Prebon arrvied at the bridge and sent a message over the ships comm.

"Everyone report to the bridge! We are now leaving for the attack!"

______________________________________________________________________
Vulois

Vulois reapeared just outside the CF. He tried to see if what Convix 
said was true.

Convix? Are you there?

No answer.

He attempted to generate energy into his palms. While he still could, 
it was no where near what he was used to. He just remembered that it 
was over, and he could continue with his life. He wanted to see 
Battera and Cybershark one more time. He went up to the ships door 
and knocked.

"Hello? I anyone there? My name is Vulois, and I must speak with 
Battera and Cybershark!"
